videos.description: Matthew Jordan run for 2-yards for a TD
videos.headline: Georgia Tech opens up the scoring with the QB Keeper

videos.description: Georgia Tech QB Justin Thomas escapes the pocket and avoids being brought down by Duke's defense running 82 yards for the touchdown.
videos.headline: Georgia Tech's Thomas' elusiveness results in 82-yard score

videos.description: Jela Duncan run for 5-yards to the GTech 33 Jela Duncan fumbled, recovered by GTech Corey Griffin
videos.headline: Georgia Tech recovers ball after Duncan fumble

videos.description: Daniel Jones pass complete to Daniel Helm for 23-yard TD
videos.headline: Helm's 1st career TD reception puts Duke on the board

videos.description: Georgia Tech QB Justin Thomas drops back and throws to an open Clinton Lynch for an easy 46-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Yellow Jackets' Thomas finds Lynch wide open for 46-yard TD

videos.description: Jela Duncan run for 57-yards to the GTech 3 Jela Duncan fumbled, forced by A.J. Gray, recovered by GTech Step Durham
videos.headline: A.J. Gray forces fumble to end Duke drive

videos.headline: Thomas airs it out to Jeune who makes the nice grab

videos.description: Justin Thomas run for 22-yards for a TD (Harrison Butker KICK)
videos.headline: Thomas goes untouched on the 22-yard score

videos.description: Ball pops out of Daniel Jones hands, after blndside hit, ball intercepted by Lawrence Austin return for no gain to the GTech 48
videos.headline: Lawrence Austin lays out to grab the INT

videos.description: Justin Thomas run for a loss of 3 yards to the GTech 45 Justin Thomas fumbled, forced by Ben Humphreys, recovered by Duke Ben Humphreys
videos.headline: Ben Humphreys strips Justin Thomas and makes the recovery

videos.description: Jela Duncan run for 1-yard for a TD
videos.headline: Duncan powers up the middle for the score
